question: Provide breaking news and news analysis articles about the Turkey-Syria earthquakes.
sql_query1:
SELECT Articles.Title 
FROM Articles
WHERE (Articles.NewsType = "Breaking News" OR Articles.NewsType = "News Analysis") AND Articles.Event = "Turkey–Syria earthquakes"
sql_query2:
SELECT Articles.Title 
FROM Articles
WHERE Articles.NewsType = "Breaking News" OR Articles.NewsType = "News Analysis" AND Articles.Event = "Turkey–Syria earthquakes"
interpretation1: What breaking news articles are about the Turkey-Syria earthquakes and what news analysis articles are about the same event?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all breaking news articles and also provide a list of news analysis articles about the Turkey-Syria earthquakes.
